SUMMARY:Planet Walk
DESCRIPTION:Explore the scale of our solar system on the Prairie Ridge Planet Walk. Along the way\, we’ll share exciting collaborative science opportunities where you can play a part in space exploration.\n\nThis program is for ages 10 and up. Please dress for the weather and be prepared to take a longer walk (about a mile\, up and down hills). We will meet at the green entrance gate.
