SUMMARY:Garden Sprouts!
DESCRIPTION:Do you have children interested in digging through the dirt and watching plants grow? This is the program for you! Intended for early childhood audiences (ages 7 and below)\, this program is designed to engage children with various hands-on\, interactive approaches to plant and garden exploration. Join us as we explore seeds\, flowers\, soil\, and the critters that help make it all work below the ground! Please note that all participants will plant seeds to take home. \nThis is a free drop-in program located at the picnic tables below the Nature PlaySpace. Staff and supplies will be available from 10:30 am to 11:30 am. Come dressed for the weather and ready to get messy!
URL:https://naturalsciences.org/calendar/event/garden-sprouts-2/
